<div class="relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://i.gyazo.com/eb43c19a6e494f485aa8f249a8ff5b59.jpg')] bg-center bg-cover opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative ">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <br>
          <h6 class="text-center">Shibattは、LINEから素早く</h6>
          <h6 class="text-center">メモを作成できるサービスです。</h6>
          <h6 class="text-center">メモは書きっぱなしにせず受動的に振り返ることで、</h6>
          <h6 class="text-center">自身の思考を整理し、行動に活かすことができます。</h6>
        <br>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <button class="btn bg-yellow-300 hover:bg-white" onclick="my_modal_6.showModal()">どんなサービス？</button>
        <dialog id="my_modal_6" class="modal modal-bottom sm:modal-middle font-handwriting">
          <div class="modal-box">
            <h3 class="font-handwriting text-lg">サービスについて</h3>
            <p class="py-4">
            <h3>思いつきで書いたメモ、散らかってませんか？</h3>
            <br>
            <h1><strong><u>コアな機能</u><strong></h1>
            <h3>・思いつきを忘れず残すために、素早くメモを作成できます</h3>
            <h3>  （LINEログイン推奨）</h3>
            <h3>・作成したメモを散らけず、紐付けて振り返りメモを作成できます</h3>
            <br>
            <h1><strong><u>開発背景</u><strong></h1>
            <h3>大量に蓄積されていくインプットで、自身のアウトプットが追いつかない</h3>
            <h3>都度書き残しているけど、まとめておらず振り返りが困難</h3>
            <h3>そんな悩みを解決するために、このサービスを作成してみようと思いました。</h3>
            </p>
            <div class="modal-action">
              <form method="dialog">
                <button class="btn">Close</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </dialog>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <button class="btn bg-white hover:bg-black-800" style="color: #E9B824;" onclick="my_modal_7.showModal()">使い方</button>
        <dialog id="my_modal_7" class="modal modal-bottom sm:modal-middle font-handwriting">
          <div class="modal-box">
            <h3 class="font-handwriting text-lg">使い方</h3>
            <p class="py-4">
            <h3>1. LINEでメッセージを送信/アプリでメモ作成ボタン</h3>
            <h3>2. メモを作成</h3>
            <h3>3. メモ一覧のチェックボックスで紐づけるメモを選択</h3>
            <h3>4. メモ一覧の振り返りメモ作成ボタンをクリック</h3>
            <h3>5. 振り返りメモを作成</h3>
            </p>
            <div class="modal-action">
              <form method="dialog">
                <button class="btn">Close</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </dialog>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="carousel carousel-center bg-neutral rounded-box max-w-md mx-auto space-x-4 p-4">
          <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
            <img
              src="https://i.gyazo.com/dce6bf974f0ccd9a7a444e3bfd6cea1c.png"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://i.gyazo.com/3a7df6cc8691bc76b26ad27e9db05e51.jpg"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1572635148818-ef6fd45eb394.webp"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1494253109108-2e30c049369b.webp"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1550258987-190a2d41a8ba.webp"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1559181567-c3190ca9959b.webp"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1601004890684-d8cbf643f5f2.webp"
              <div class="carousel-item", style="width: 350px; height: 500px;" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
          <br>
          <div class="skeleton h-60 w-180 flex flex-col items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #CCE0AC;">
            <h3>まずはLINEお友達登録!!</h3>
            <h3>ShibattへLINEでメッセージを送信→メモを作成</h3>
            <img src="https://qr-official.line.me/sid/L/023jcczr.png" alt="LINE QRコード" width="80">
            <a href="https://line.me/R/ti/p/%40023jcczr" class="btn btn-outline btn-accent">
              Shibatt公式LINE 友達追加URL
            </a>
          </div>
          <br>
          <div class="divider divider"></div>
          <h6 class="text-center text-xl mb-6">ログイン</h6>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <%= link_to oauth_path(provider: :line) do %>
              <%= image_tag "line_login.png", class: "h-15 w-40 opacity-70" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="divider divider" style="border-left: none;">OR</div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center ">
            <div class="w-full max-w-xs">

            <%= form_with(url: login_path, local: true) do |f| %>
              <label class="input input-bordered flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 16 16"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="h-4 w-4 opacity-70">
                  <path
                    d="M8 8a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6ZM12.735 14c.618 0 1.093-.561.872-1.139a6.002 6.002 0 0 0-11.215 0c-.22.578.254 1.139.872 1.139h9.47Z" />
                </svg>
                <%= f.text_field :username, class: "grow", placeholder: "username" %>
              </label>
                  
              <label class="input input-bordered flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 16 16"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="h-4 w-4 opacity-70">
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M14 6a4 4 0 0 1-4.899 3.899l-1.955 1.955a.5.5 0 0 1-.353.146H5v1.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-2a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-2.293a.5.5 0 0 1 .146-.353l3.955-3.955A4 4 0 1 1 14 6Zm-4-2a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0 2 2 0 0 0-2-2Z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <%= f.password_field :password, class: "grow", placeholder: "password" %>
              </label>
              <div class="text-right"><%= f.submit "ログイン", class: "btn btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg" %></div>      
            <% end %>
          </div>
                    
        </div>
      </div>
                    
      </dialog>
                                        
      <br>
      <div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center flex-col lg:flex-row">
        <div class="card rounded-box grid h-auto flex-grow place-items-center">
            <% if @user %>
              <dialog id="my_modal_5" class="modal modal-bottom sm:modal-middle">
                <div class="modal-box">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">メモ作成</h3>
                  <%= form_with model: @memo, url: user_memos_path(@user), local: true do |f| %>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <%= f.text_area :content, class: "form-control", placeholder: "メモ内容", rows: 5 %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <%= f.submit "作成", class: "btn" %>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                  <div class="modal-action">
                    <form method="dialog">
                      <!-- if there is a button in form, it will close the modal -->
                      <button class="btn">Close</button>
                    </form>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </dialog>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <h6>Progress</h6>
                <div class="radial-progress" style="--value:<%= @progress_rate[:in_progress] %>;" role="progressbar">
                  <%= @progress_rate[:in_progress] %>%
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex space-x-4 bg-transparent">
                <%= link_to "【memo】", user_memos_path(current_user), class: "bg-white text-green-800 px-4 py-2 rounded" if current_user %>
                <%= link_to "【ref_memo】", reflection_memos_path, class: "bg-white text-green-800 px-4 py-2 rounded" if current_user %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
            <br>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
                  
      <% if @user %>
        <div class="toast toast-end">
          <button class="btn bg-teal-800 text-white hover:bg-teal-900" onclick="my_modal_5.showModal()">【メモ作成】</button>
          <%= link_to '先週の振り返り', new_lastweek_reflection_memos_path, class: "btn text-teal-800 bg-white hover:bg-teal-200" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>